id isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/us-open-day-three-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟和中国启动促进工业数据流动的机制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-china-launch-mechanism-facilitate-industrial-data-flows-2024-08-28/</link><description>欧盟在周三的一份声明中表示，欧盟和中国在旨在简化跨境数据流动的新体系下启动了首次讨论。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 11:38:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/eu-china-launch-mechanism-facilitate-industrial-data-flows-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，制药商萌蒂的中国业务出售未能找到买家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drugmaker-mundipharmas-china-unit-sale-fails-find-buyer-sources-say-2024-08-28/</link><description>两位知情人士称，亿万富翁萨克勒家族旗下的制药商萌蒂国际制药公司在今年的重新出售过程中第二次未能为其中国子公司找到买家。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 11:04:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/drugmaker-mundipharmas-china-unit-sale-fails-find-buyer-sources-say-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>香港开发商押注中国需求，转向租赁市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/betting-chinese-demand-hong-kong-developers-turn-rental-market-2024-08-28/</link><description>一些香港开发商现在转向住房租赁和租赁市场，以应对房地产市场的长期低迷，并满足中国内地专业人士和学生不断增长的租赁需求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 08:05:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/betting-chinese-demand-hong-kong-developers-turn-rental-market-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>又有两家中国航空公司开始运营中国商飞C919客机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/two-more-chinese-airlines-start-flying-china-made-comac-c919-jet-2024-08-28/</link><description>据官方媒体中央电视台报道，国航和南航周三接收首架飞机后，将成为第二家和第三家运营中国商飞 C919 客机的中国航空公司。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 07:11:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/two-more-chinese-airlines-start-flying-china-made-comac-c919-jet-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>澳门法官宣布竞逐世界最大赌场中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/macau-judge-announces-bid-lead-worlds-biggest-casino-hub-2024-08-28/</link><description>澳门高级法官岑豪辉周三宣布，他打算在 10 月份竞选澳门行政长官，因为世界上最大的赌博中心正在努力将自己转变为主要的区域旅游目的地。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 03:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/macau-judge-announces-bid-lead-worlds-biggest-casino-hub-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达财报和美国经济数据公布前股市持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-28/</link><description>周三，在芯片制造商英伟达盘后发布季度收益报告以及本周晚些时候的经济数据之前，全球股市走软，而美元反弹。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 02:22:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>中美官员讨论拜登和习近平新一轮会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-holds-2nd-day-talks-taiwan-fentanyl-with-top-biden-aide-2024-08-28/</link><description>周三，中美两国高级官员在北京举行的高层会议上表示，两国总统讨论了在不久的将来举行新的会谈。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 02:17:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-holds-2nd-day-talks-taiwan-fentanyl-with-top-biden-aide-2024-08-28/</guid></item><item><title>网络安全公司称，中国黑客利用漏洞危害互联网公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-exploited-bug-compromise-internet-companies-cybersecurity-firm-2024-08-27/</link><description>一家网络安全公司周二表示，一个中国黑客组织利用一个软件漏洞入侵了美国和国外的多家互联网公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 16:38:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/chinese-hackers-exploited-bug-compromise-internet-companies-cybersecurity-firm-2024-08-27/</guid></item><item><title>尼日利亚蒂努布将访华寻求经济合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nigerias-tinubu-visit-china-seeking-economic-cooperation-2024-08-27/</link><description>尼日利亚政府发言人周二表示，尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布将于下周访华期间会见中国国家主席习近平，讨论经济、农业和卫星技术合作。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 16:11:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/nigerias-tinubu-visit-china-seeking-economic-cooperation-2024-08-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大的电动汽车部门警告上半年减值拨备损失更大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-evergrandes-ev-arm-warns-bigger-loss-first-half-2024-08-27/</link><description>陷入困境的房地产开发商中国恒大旗下的电动汽车部门周二表示，预计 2024 年上半年将出现更大亏损，反映出减值准备增加。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 15:21:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-evergrandes-ev-arm-warns-bigger-loss-first-half-2024-08-27/</guid></item><item><title>印度太阳能电池板因可能与中国强迫劳动有关而面临美国审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/indian-solar-panels-face-us-scrutiny-possible-links-china-forced-labor-2024-08-27/</link><description>根据该机构的数据，自 10 月以来，美国海关和边境保护局根据 2022 年禁止强迫劳动制造商品的法律，扣留了来自印度的近 4300 万美元的电子设备，这成为该贸易执法机构的新焦点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 11:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/indian-solar-panels-face-us-scrutiny-possible-links-china-forced-labor-2024-08-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>